DATA NOTICE
-----------
This repository contains code that ingests public data from Korean government
sources (산림청, 한국임업진흥원, 한국산림복지진흥원, 한국등산·트레킹지원센터, 법제처,
국토교통부, KOSIS, 농촌진흥청 etc.) under the 공공누리(KOGL) Type 1 license
with attribution.

Forest policy answers generated by this system MUST cite the original legal
provisions and page numbers. Decisions with legal or financial consequences
should be verified through official channels:
  - 산지전용통합정보시스템: 1644-0672
  - 산림탄소센터: 042-603-7315
  - 한국임업진흥원: 1600-3248
  - 산림조합중앙회: 1544-7170

